{"context":"","status":200,"data":{"id":16,"microcosmId":1,"title":"Adding this item should update the item count on the home page","comments":{"total":2000,"limit":25,"offset":50,"maxOffset":100,"totalPages":5,"page":1,"links":[{"rel":"self","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16"},{"rel":"next","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16?offset=75"},{"rel":"prev","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16?offset=25"},{"rel":"first","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16?offset=0"},{"rel":"last","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16?offset=100"}],"type":"/api/v1/comments","items":[{"id":116,"itemType":"conversation","itemId":16,"revisions":1,"inReplyTo":0,"attachments":0,"firstLine":"","markdown":"It doesn't seem to update the number of views but I expect that comment count has been implemented, so that should go to 1 after this comment.","html":"\u003cp\u003eIt doesn&#39;t seem to update the number of views but I expect that comment count has been implemented, so that should go to 1 after this comment.\u003c/p\u003e","meta":{"created":"2013-05-06T10:37:18.148497Z","createdBy":{"id":22,"userId":22,"profileName":"oliver.schick","visible":false,"gravatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8676a142071335db414962d61103d47","meta":{"links":[{"rel":"self","href":"/api/v1/profiles/22"},{"rel":"site","href":"/api/v1/sites/1"}]}},"flags":{"deleted":false,"moderated":false,"visible":false},"links":[{"rel":"self","href":"/api/v1/comments/16"},{"rel":"conversation","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16"},{"rel":"up","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16"}]}},{"id":117,"itemType":"conversation","itemId":16,"revisions":1,"inReplyTo":0,"attachments":0,"firstLine":"","markdown":"Hang on, it did update views, but only after a delay (which I think is what you said on the LFGSS thread).","html":"\u003cp\u003eHang on, it did update views, but only after a delay (which I think is what you said on the LFGSS thread).\u003c/p\u003e","meta":{"created":"2013-05-06T10:37:59.313882Z","createdBy":{"id":22,"userId":22,"profileName":"oliver.schick","visible":false,"gravatar":"https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e8676a142071335db414962d61103d47","meta":{"links":[{"rel":"self","href":"/api/v1/profiles/22"},{"rel":"site","href":"/api/v1/sites/1"}]}},"flags":{"deleted":false,"moderated":false,"visible":false},"links":[{"rel":"self","href":"/api/v1/comments/16"},{"rel":"conversation","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16"},{"rel":"up","href":"/api/v1/conversations/16"}]}},{"id":169,"itemType":"conversation","itemId":16,"revisions":1,"inReplyTo":0,"attachments":0,"firstLine":"","markdown":"Yeah it does the view count update in batches.\r\n\r\nIt updates item counts (shown on the home page) instantly.\r\n\r\nIt updates comment counts (shown on the home page and the Microcosm page) instantly.\r\n\r\nIt updates view counts (shown on the Microcosm page) every 30 seconds (currently).\r\n\r\nThe reason for the view counts being updated in batches? Right now over 1,300 people are actively reading stuff on LFGSS... 1,300 updates to view counts? Yup, but to prevent the caches being useless we do it in batches so that even when a thread is getting hammered it's still cached for at least 30 seconds.","html":"\u003cp\u003eYeah it does the view count update in batches.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt updates item counts (shown on the home page) instantly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt updates comment counts (shown on the home page and the Microcosm page) instantly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIt updates view counts (shown on the Microcosm page) every 30 seconds (currently).\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe reason for the view counts being updated in batches? Right now over 1,300 people are actively reading stuff on LFGSS... 1,300 updates to view counts? Yup, but to prevent the caches being useless we do it in batches so that even when a thread is getting hammered it&#39;s still cached for at least 30 seconds.\u003c/p\u003e","meta":{"created":"2013-05-06T21:40:18.366838Z","createdBy":{"id":2,"userId":2,"profileName":"Velocio",